##Under the ANTI-"epidemic" , how to break the situation safely when enterprises resume work?

Wechat, chinanewsweekly

Function introduction, here is "China News weekly" the head of the weekly gentleman, the influence has the influence you. Come with me to break through the fog, to find the truth, to watch the Times.

After the pause, reboot safely

"according to the plan made a year ago, the order was shipped immediately after the start of construction on January 31. Now not only are the old orders delayed, but other businesses are basically suspended, " said Lin Hao, the owner of a machine tool parts factory, the biggest impact of the outbreak on factories is production capacity and logistics, followed by the increasingly tight financial chain, "production stopped, but equipment, rent and labor, every day is an expense! "

He said that around the same small and medium-sized manufacturers in the Pearl River Delta situation is similar, "this year has been difficult. "

In order to prevent and control the epidemic, to avoid large-scale population movements and gathering, this year's Spring Festival holiday extended, enterprises and factories have been repeatedly delayed to resume work. Perhaps years from now, when we think of the sudden "Black Swan" of the 2020s, the first thing we think of is the pause button that seems to have been pressed invisibly, and the slow restart that follows.

"survive. "

As of February 18, the cumulative number of confirmed cases of new coronavirus pneumonia in the country exceeded seventy-two thousand, the epidemic remains serious. The good news is that the number of new confirmed cases in all regions except Hubei has fallen by 14 in a row, falling to double digits for the first time. At the same time as the epidemic prevention and control entered a new stage, it is imperative to restore production and stabilize the economy.

According to the data, economic indicators in both consumption and investment have fallen sharply as a result of the outbreak. In particular, catering, hotel tourism, entertainment, Film and Television, retail and transportation industries are hit hard.

According to statistics, the box office of the 2019 Spring Festival stall was 5.859 billion yuan. This year's Spring Festival stalls and New Year stalls in front of the upper house have withdrawn stalls, many theaters temporarily closed, box office revenue bleak. Chinese films earned just 1.81 million yuan at the box office on the first day of the Lunar New Year, according to Cat's eye professional edition.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Want to cry without tears is not only the cinema line, the population flow control affects the offline consumption in all directions. A number of large-scale shopping malls across the country closed, a number of restaurant chains also announced the closure of brands.

Xibei naked face village Chairman Jia Guolong said that Xibei naked face village in more than 60 cities owned more than 400 chain stores have basically closed, the only take-away business can only reach 5%-10% of normal revenue. In previous years, Xibei's overall revenue of about 700-800 million yuan, this year almost all return to zero.

Zhu Wuxiang, a professor of finance at the School of Economics and management at Tsinghua University, and Wei Wei, a professor of management at Peking University's HSBC School of business, released data on the impact of the epidemic on Small and medium-sized enterprises and how to deal with it, 31.08 percent of businesses expect revenue to decline by more than 50 percent in 2020, and 58.88 percent by more than 20 percent.

At the same time, 35.96 percent of the companies lasted only one month, and only 9.27 percent lasted six months or longer. If the outbreak lasts more than six months, 90% of businesses are likely to go out of business or go bankrupt.

"Survive" , become business owner face 2020 first goal.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Wu Hai, founder of the Orange Crystal Hotel, said the government did not need to worry about confidence in the market, the job was to try to help us "live" until the end of the epidemic.

Up to now, the Ministry of Finance, the Central Bank, the Ministry of Commerce and other multi-ministerial relief, from financial subsidies, loans, taxes, social security and other aspects to support enterprises to tide over the epidemic.

"In the current epidemic environment, the most important thing for enterprises is the issue of capital chain, " Liu Shangxi, president of the China Academy of Financial Sciences, said in an interview, finance and finance have introduced a number of policies, such as loan interest discount, the key is to implement.

Classified Prevention and control is the key

Of course, preferential subsidies for small and medium-sized enterprises can only solve the immediate problem. In the end, the epidemic will pass, life will continue, to solve the fundamental survival of enterprises have to rely on the resumption of work and production, and epidemic prevention and control phase of the gradual resumption of work has become a common challenge for the government and enterprises.

On February 8, the State Council's Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism for the COVID-19 of pneumonia issued the notice on effectively strengthening the scientific prevention and control of the epidemic and doing a good job of resuming work and resuming production in an orderly manner, it is required to formulate a plan for the resumption of work by categories and batches, especially in the areas of epidemic prevention and control, energy supply, transportation and logistics, which involve important national economy and people's livelihood, and to ensure conditions for prompt resumption of work. Create an enabling environment for qualified industries and enterprises to speed up the resumption of work.

On Feb. 10, work began to resume across the country, and the epidemic continues, with many businesses still struggling to get back to work.

The boss of a daily chemical factory admits that many production lines can not start because of road closures in the hometown of some migrant workers. It is understood that many enterprises are facing the stage of difficult employment. In addition to the shortage of rework personnel, some enterprises also face the problem of lack of protective materials, which directly affects the safety and health of employees during the rework period.

In response, the National Development and Reform Commission proposed to promote orderly return to work in batches, while reducing the density of people in the workplace through staggered peak hours, flexible working arrangements and other means, establish and improve the daily cleaning, disinfection, ventilation, temperature monitoring system.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On February 12, the Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China held a meeting to point out that non epidemic prevention and control key areas to implement the division, classification and precise prevention and control as the key to coordinate epidemic prevention and control and the restoration of economic and social order.

China's epidemic prevention work is at a critical stage, but the recovery of production also deserves attention, said Zhu Lijia, a professor in the Department of Public Administration at the National School of Administration. At present, the epidemic situation is not the same in every area of our country, and the prevention and control at different levels is the embodiment of different prevention and control within an administrative area.

Under the idea of "grading prevention and control" , in view of the health and safety problems of employees during the rework period, the NDRC specially proposed that grading and classification enhance the ability of rapid screening such as nucleic acid detection. Under the premise of ensuring safety, the observation time of medical observation and isolated people at home should be set up scientifically by using the technology such as the detection of foot nucleic acid.

The COVID-19 has a wide range of in vitro diagnostic reagents, including nucleic acids, antigens and antibody diagnostic reagents. Currently, in addition to nucleic acid reagents, it is used in the diagnosis of COVID-19 infections, antibody diagnostic reagents are also under development.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
On February 12, at a press conference on the prevention and control of the epidemic in Guangdong Province, the provincial health and health commission said that the province's fever clinics had started screening for nucleic acid testing of patients, and the scope had been extended to all staff members. For All patients attending fever clinics, throat swabs were collected for nucleic acid testing.

In addition, the COVID-19 of Jinan High Tech Zone in Shandong Province also issued a notice on the development of nucleic acid testing service enterprises, to make it clear that enterprises can voluntarily test their employees for COVID-19 nucleic acid.

It is undeniable that in the critical period of resuming work and production, all nucleic acid detection and investigation has become a critical point to guard the achievements of epidemic prevention and control. In particular, for some cases of new coronavirus infection in a longer period of time without obvious symptoms, in addition to the medical system, but also to introduce a professional level of social medical institutions for screening.

The worst fear is asymptomatic carriers, Zhang Zuofeng, associate dean of the Public Health at Ucla and a longtime professor of epidemiology, told Chinese philanthropist in an interview, if there is a strict re-work prevention and control conditions, it can also avoid the epidemic disease after re-work.

"On February 9, we launched a 'nucleic acid testing solution for employees to return to work during the outbreak' , " said a person in charge of aikang group, "The group's medical institutions will arrange and organize the third-party testing institutions that have been incorporated into the government-designated COVID-19 nucleic acid test to take throat swab samples from employees at the locations designated by customers in strict accordance with the relevant national requirements, and the relevant service procedures will be developed in accordance with the requirements of local governments. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Prior to this, the government issued a text initiative and encourage third-party testing agencies to participate in nucleic acid testing, prevention and control of the epidemic to provide technical support and service guarantees. Industry insiders believe that the third-party testing organizations with professional advantages to provide testing for enterprises and reduce the risk of staff cross-infection resulting in work stoppage and production stoppage are effective measures to prevent and control at different levels at present.

It is reported that Aikang group has cooperated with local governments in the designated third-party testing agencies to provide "during the outbreak of nucleic acid testing solutions for employees to resume work, " Through nucleic acid detection to help enterprises "early detection, early isolation" potential virus infection, reduce the risk of corporate cluster infection, has been in many cities.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
"Even if the world is as barren as the plague in the small city of Oran, as long as there is a trace of warmth, despair will not devour people's hearts. " As Albert Camus says in "the plague, " the epidemic will pass, and spring is at hand. Under the graded protection system, many parties are jointly building a "protective wall" to ensure safety for the resumption of work.
